The paper deals with the problem of web bot detection, which is a subfield of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed solution involves the use of convolutional neural networks (CNN), which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of big data, which is a topic in both data science (cs.DS) and systems and control (cs.SI). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR, followed by cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI, and cs.DS.
